      <longTitle>
        <p>Amendment to the <ref href="/akn/poc/bill/paella-reform-2024">Paella Reform Bill</ref>: <docTitle>Inclusion of Brown Rice</docTitle></p>
      </longTitle>
      <p>Submitted by <docProponent>Representative Naturist</docProponent> to the <ref href="/akn/poc/bill/paella-reform-2024">Paella Reform Bill</ref>.</p>
    </preface>

    <amendmentBody>
      <amendmentContent>
        <block name="amendment">
          <p>It is proposed to amend <ref href="/akn/poc/act/valencian-paella-recipe#art_1">Article 1</ref> to include brown rice as a healthy alternative:</p>
          <p><mod>"Article 1. Type of rice. 400 grams of bomba rice, medium-grain round rice, or brown rice shall be used. Bomba rice is preferably recommended when available."</mod></p>
        </block>
        <block name="justification">
          <p>Brown rice provides greater nutritional value, fiber, and minerals. Its inclusion promotes healthier eating habits without altering the spirit of the recipe.</p>
        </block>
      </amendmentContent>
